#AD #WBSponsored Fire 🔥 & ICE 🧊 who is your favorite MK fighter? • A Collaboration with @Mortalkombat #mkkollective #MK1
.
I'm stoked to be a part of the MK Kollective again, and this time working on a tribute piece to the sworn enemies turned brothers and allies,
Sub Zero and Scorpion! In the new Mortal Kombat game, you choose a main fighter and also an assist character so the Lin Kuei brothers 
can have each others backs even in-game. The characters' color palettes and elements are such a contrast to each other that I've opted for
a very limited color palette to maintain a clean and mean look. 
.
The new Mortal Kombat drops on on September 19th! 
.
.
#Mortalkombat #illustration #artwork #characterdesign #art
